<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>決済完了 - gibtee</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
    .container {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 400px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .success-icon {
      color: #27AE60;
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    p {
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .order-number {
      background: #f8f8f8;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .close-button {
      background: #27AE60;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 10px;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .close-button:hover {
      background: #219653;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="success-icon">✓</div>
    <h1>お支払いが完了しました</h1>
    <p>ご注文いただきありがとうございます。お支払いの処理が完了しました。</p>
    <div class="order-number">
      注文番号: <%= orderNumber %>
    </div>
    <p>配送状況はLINEでお知らせします。</p>
    <button class="close-button" onclick="window.close()">閉じる</button>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
